ovar&amp;rft.au=Ostovar%2C+Afshon+P.&amp;rft.btitle=Guardians+of+the+Islamic+Revolution+Ideology%2C+Politics%2C+and+the+Development+of+Military+Power+in+Iran+%281979%E2%80%932009%29&amp;rft.date=2009&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fdeepblue.lib.umich.edu%2Fbitstream%2Fhandle%2F2027.42%2F64683%2Fafshon_1.pdf%3Bjsessionid%3DDF7BFA33BF18FF73E9117CB0504F14E1%3Fsequence%3D1&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Michigan&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-milani-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-milani_12-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><span class=\"citation book\">Abbas Milani (31 July 2010). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://books.google.com/books?id=YTrRom48fhAC&amp;pg=PA123\"><i>The Myth of the Great Satan: A New Look at America's Relations with Iran</i></a>. Hoover Press. p.&#160;122. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-8179-1136-2\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-8179-1136-2\">978-0-8179-1136-2</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">1 August</span> 2013</span>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAli+Shariati&amp;rft.au=Abbas+Milani&amp;rft.aulast=Abbas+Milani&amp;rft.btitle=The+Myth+of+the+Great+Satan%3A+A+New+Look+at+America%27s+Relations+with+Iran&amp;rft.date=31+July+2010&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DYTrRom48fhAC%26pg%3DPA123&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-8179-1136-2&amp;rft.pages=122&amp;rft.pub=Hoover+Press&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-13\">^</a></b></spa